Content-Type: text/plain; charset=us-ascii; format=flowed

Invoice from Mary for October.

SW

From: Grants <grants@townofpaonia.com>
Sent: Thursday, October 31, 2024 2:30 PM
To: Stefen Wynn <StefenW@townofpaonia.com>
Subject: eopc for 5th and Grand

After pulling out my hair, I finally realized the EOPC for 5th and Grand dated 7-11-2024 is off by $17. The budget I calculated and their figures didn't match but when I added their items in the detail, I got $2,543,517 not $2,543,500 as stated on the front sheet, exactly what I submitted. Just an FYI.

Also attached is my invoice for October.

Mary

Mary Bachran
Grant Writer, Town of Paonia

--_000_DM6PR12MB5005E5ED558B0F18822C43EBDE512DM6PR12MB5005namp_
